column2: Cold-cloudy and a all day mist.  pretty strong wind from the sw and no other boats out.
Nice clear morning with just a little breeze from the so. but is picking up.  No other boats on the lake and see only one loon- yesterday there were two.  The geese are gathering.
Cloudy-overcast with slight wind.  The second loon is back.  One other boat on the lake and the lake is greening up from the algae
The lake is greening up along the shore.  Very nice sunny day with a little wind from the So.  No other boats on the lake.  No fish biting either but that is ok.
Blue skies- no wind and 60 degrees.  beautiful day and alone on the lake.
Clear skies-little wind from the east and 35 degrees.  Fishing very slow. No other boats on the lake.  The water is pretty green from algia.
Very damp-hazy and a temp of 40 degrees. slight wind out of the SW and no other boats on the lake.  Boats and docks are being removed from the lake.
cloudy-light wind from the S.W. and no other boats on the lake
Slight wind from the so. Family of four loons on the lake.  Clouding over.
clear skies-very light wind from the north-otter busy on east shore- family of loons on the lake and no other boats out.  Wonderful morning.
Partly cloudy with a nice breeze from the So.  No one else on the lake
sunny day-50 degrees and slight breeze from the so.
Cloud cover- very little wind.  Bugs on the water.  Otherwise nice.
Sunny- light breeze from the north.  One other boat on the lake.
Sunny- light breeze.  Had the lake to myself.  Temps reaching the 50s.
